                    </svg>
                    <span id="socialText">Google+로 로그인하기</span>

                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="naver">
                <a href="/auth/facebook" class='btn btn-info'>
                    <span id="facebookIcon" style="color: green;"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f fa-lg"></i></span>
                    <span id="socialText">네이버로 로그인하기</span>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="kakaotalk">
                <a href="/auth/kakao" class='btn btn-info'>
                    <span id="facebookIcon" style="color: yellow;"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f fa-lg"></i></span>
                    <span id="socialText">카카오 계정으로 로그인하기</span>
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>

        <span>아직 계정이 없으신가요?
        <a href="/auth/register" class="member-register-link" id="registerhagi">
        <span style="color:#F9C700;">가입하기</span>
        <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right"></i></a></span>
    </div>
</div>
</center>

